<!--index.wxml-->
<view class="bg-black">
  <view class="page-body">
    <form catchsubmit="formSubmit" catchreset="formReset">
    <view class="bg-img bg-mask padding-tb-xl" style="background-image: url('/resource/Bg01.png');height: 1200rpx;">
      <view class="padding-xl text-white">
        <view class="padding text-sl text-bold">
          <text>预测卜问得先知\n我命由我不由天</text> 
        </view>
        <view class="padding text-xl">
          Predict the prophet, my life is from me, not from heaven!
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="text-center text-shadow text-orange text-xxl text-bold">时间起卦</view>
      <view class="padding text-center">
        <view class="padding text-xl text-yellow">
          <text>{{nowyear}}年</text>
          <text>{{nowmonth}}月</text>
          <text>{{nowday}}日</text>
          <text>{{nowhour}}时</text>
          <text>{{nowminute}}分</text>
          <text>{{nowsecond}}秒</text>
        </view>
        <view class="text-lg">
          <text>农历：{{showganzhi}}年 {{showlunarmonth}}月{{showlunarday}} {{showfrombirth}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="padding flex flex-direction">
        <button class="cu-btn bg-grey lg" formType="reset">获取时间</button>
        <button class="cu-btn bg-red margin-tb-sm lg" formType="submit">开始排盘</button>
      </view>
      <view class="text-center text-red text-sm">
        <text>
          不诚不占：此乃求教于神明，首重真诚。\n不义不占：不合乎正当性及合理性的问题不必占问。\n不疑不占：必须是理性难以测度之事。
        </text>
      </view>
    </view>
    </form>
  </view>

</view>
